description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Bank Receptionist to work at our busy GP Walk In Centre, 15 Katie Road, Selly Oak, Birmingham B29 6JG during the hours of 8pm-11pm Sunday - Monday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will be on a Bank contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require reliable, punctual and trustworthy individual to provide face to face point of contact for patients and act as a point of communication between patients, doctors and other medical staff; data entry of patient details, answer the telephone and other related tasks. Excellent attention to detail and customer service skills are a must.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential requirements: Previous experience of working in a similar environment or as a medical receptionist. Must have previous experience with Adastra, the abilty to multi-task, confident with computers, and a good telephone manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Must be proficient in reading and writing English with an understanding, acceptance and adherance to the need for strict confidentiality and a willingness to undergo a DBS (previously CRB) check.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply as soon as possible as the vacancy will close early if a high volume of applications is received.&lt;/p&gt;
